comments: Horford (PHI) sets the screen on Wiggins (GSW) and absorbs the contact.
Wiggins (GSW) makes contact with Harris's (PHI) arm and affects his driving shot attempt.
Robinson III (PHI) initiates contact to Lee's (GSW) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Chriss (GSW) sets the screen on Robinson III (PHI) and absorbs the contact.
Harris (PHI) and Mulder (GSW) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Harris (PHI) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Lee (GSW) sets the screen on Horford (PHI) and absorbs the contact.
Horford (PHI) wraps Chriss (GSW) as he attempts to disengage from the pick.
Paschall (GSW) draws Scott (PHI) into the air towards him. This results in a foul on Scott even if contact is initiated by Paschall.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position on Harris (PHI) in the post.
Harris (PHI) and Toscano-Anderson (GSW) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Chriss (GSW) makes contact with the ball prior to the ball making contact with the backboard.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) makes marginal contact with Harris (PHI) in the post.
Chriss (GSW) briefly places his arm around Scott (PHI) before correcting.
Milton (PHI) commits a take foul on Mulder (GSW).
Milton (PHI) commits a take foul on Mulder (GSW).
Paschall (GSW) and Harris (PHI) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Harris (PHI).
